WEBVTT

00:02:29.338 --> 00:02:32.097
that can actually define their role

00:02:32.097 --> 00:02:34.182
in society

00:02:34.182 --> 00:02:35.826
in terms of a much larger purpose

00:02:35.826 --> 00:02:38.657
than the products and brands that they sell.

00:02:38.657 --> 00:02:41.890
And companies that actually define a true north,

00:02:41.890 --> 00:02:43.636
things that are nonnegotiable

00:02:43.636 --> 00:02:46.196
whether times are good, bad, ugly --

00:02:46.196 --> 00:02:47.463
doesn't matter.

00:02:47.463 --> 00:02:49.629
There are things that you stand for.

00:02:49.629 --> 00:02:54.121
Values and purpose are going to be the two

00:02:54.121 --> 00:02:56.256
drivers of software

00:02:56.256 --> 00:02:57.968
that are going to create

00:02:57.968 --> 00:03:00.034
the companies of tomorrow.